	   <tr><td colspan=2>Weapons are no longer a matter of choice.&nbsp;&nbsp;Any monk can do fine without them until he decides to visit Kunark.  So many of my friend's have quit because we were told that nothing would be better than our fists and yet here we are being told something different.  It was a sad day when I had to semi-retire my primary because he didn't belong to an uberguild camping the dungeons in Kunark...<br><br>My second monk is working on his blunt skills (both) and his usual pattern is max out h2h first, then go to the blunts (first 1hb then 2hb).  Even though he is packing extra weight, the ac loss is still minor at 22 and he is swiftly nearing mastery in his skills.<br><br>I would recommend that if you do plan to visit Kunark and probably Velious when it arrives, work hard on those blunts.  <br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
